value: Take 1 list and have some objects inside it as sample data given below, and create a new list with unique values and console the unique values list.

title: solution
value:
const list = [{ "first": "1", "second": "2", "third": "1", "four": "5", "five": "5", "six": "9", "seven": "7" }]
let uniques_list = [];
for (i of list) {
for (j in i) {
if (!uniques_list.includes(i[j])) {
uniques_list.push(i[j]);
}
}
}
console.log(uniques_list);
